### HEALTH CHECK
GET http://localhost:5000/
Accept: application/json

### REGISTER CUSTOMER
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Customer",
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "customer",
  "phoneNumber": "9999999999",
  "address": "Customer Street 1",
  "credit": 100
}

