### GET CUSTOMER PROFILE (replace <CUSTOMER_ID>)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/<CUSTOMER_ID>
Accept: application/json

### UPDATE CUSTOMER PROFILE
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/<CUSTOMER_ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "New Customer Address",
  "phoneNumber": "1111111111"
}

